				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1845866">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							this is the first time I've actually sweated from hot sauce.<br />
<br />
I keep a bottle of Dave's Ghost Pepper sauce at work. I keep one at the house as well. I even have a picture of the Simpson's Coyote taped to the fucker just because it amuses me.  I use it on almost everything.<br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px">
