<br />
But this? This is an entirely new animal.<br />
<br />
Holy crap is this great.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Daves-Gourmet-Scorpion-Pepper-Sauce/dp/B004QO5E0M" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.amazon.com/Daves-Gourmet-.../dp/B004QO5E0M</a><br />
<br />
First time I've actually sweated from hot sauce intake in YEARS.<br />
<br />
This is either at joke level (for people who want to be cruel to others) or for enthusiasts.<br />
<br />
I put a teaspoon into my salsa and found myself unable to concentrate on anything else but the burn and the taste.<br />
<br />
Positively glorious.<br />
<br />
I will be using this sparingly, but I will be enjoying it when I do.<br />
<br />
If anyone out here likes hot sauce, I recommend this one highly.
